channel.title: I have no clue what's going on
channel.description: Okay i will admit I am an idiot when it comes to computers. All I'm here to do is play some fun hacked rs and everytime I try to run a server that has an online time of "100%" it always gives me errors like exceptions, "Error connecting to server", "loginserver is down, please try again in 1 minuete",ect. Can anyone here tell me what i have to do? I downloaded moparscape 3.2 w/ Aryan already.

item.title: I have no clue what's going on
item.dc:creator: @iz3_legend iz3 legend
item.description:
@iz3_legend wrote:

the moparscape cannot support newer servers, go to the serverstatus page and click a server either use a webclient if it has one, or download the desktop client. For the desktop client you would have to use winrar to extract it. Just google winrar and dl it its a free safe software
